{"tid":1339830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[圖] 元朗鄉黑襲擊回家途人情況持續惡化","createTime":"2019-07-21T15:33:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:33:42.000Z","uid":281025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49ec9c6b4c499736c4eb2b624454aa1dfa39922a","tid":1339830,"uid":281025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:33:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/21/232159_f146cbde28b9b1fcb9eb198fbd120851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F21%2F232159_f146cbde28b9b1fcb9eb198fbd120851.jpg&h=bdce21ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依家仲擦卡入埋站用竹枝木條毆打返緊屋企既巴打絲打。猖狂到連口罩都唔帶，擺明車馬襲擊途人 。一個半鐘前已有人報左警，但警察故意冇派人到現場阻止黑社會施襲。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">警黑兩者果然係有默契嘅「蛇鼠一窩」！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}